rComments: Professor Nosedal is really enthusiastic about teaching and always tries to create an engaging learning environment. He is also very approachable as a person, so don't shy away from asking him questions during his office hours.

He's the best prof ever! He makes sure that you understand the concepts clearly and puts an effort into explaining it to you. Also, his lectures and his handwriting is super organized. And the best thing is he knows everybody's names. But he's not an easy grader, so you have to make sure you understand everything thoroughly to get a good grade.
Professor Nosdeal is an awesome professor. He has great enthusiasm in teaching, and he tries his best to involve every student in his classes.
Go to lectures and you will know what he wants for you to know on tests and assignments. Easy class if you are willing to pay attention.

Terrible at teaching think twice before you take might convert the like for stats to a dislike to stats if keep going to classes. The classes are useless everything covered in the book not helpful at all. I would never recommend anyone to take the course with this professor. Makes you go to sleep in class.
